Main Readme 

Installation 

1. Install Docker desktop: https://www.docker.com/products/docker-desktop.

2. git clone this repository. 

3. change directory to /dublin_bus_app in terminal.

4. execute docker-compose up, then check http://localhost:8000/ 


Local developing enviroment setting

1. pip install requirement.txt to conda virtual environment: 
  - pip install -r ./requirement.txt
2. After develop on local machine if there are some new dependency, update the requirement.txt
  - pip freeze > requirement.txt
